column5: *Dynamic Inventory* - INQUIRE FIRST-  *There maybe a cleaning fee of $95 if the booking request is for 5 days or less.*  Two Bedroom: King in master, two full beds in second bedroom, sleeper sofa in living area. Maximum occupancy is 8. High season rates are: Weekend : $295 Weekday : $225  The current rate on the calendar will be valid if the booking request is within 5 days of arrival.
